All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
Boss
This class inherits the abstract entity class, which is used to create a boss object.
BossLevel
This class inherits from the abstract class Level, implementing a level with a boss.
BurstFirePowerUp
This class inherits the abstract PowerUp class, implementing the ability for the spaceship to shoot three lasers in different directions.
DukeApplicationTest
This class acts as an intermediary between an OpenJFX application and TestFX.
Enemy
This class inherits the abstract entity class, which is used to create an enemy object.
EnemyLevel
This class inherits from the abstract class Level, implementing a level with enemies similar to Space Invaders.
Entity
This is an abstract class that is used to create all types of entities used in this game.
Fireball
This class inherits the abstract Projectile class, implementing more powerful projectiles with a fireball image.
Game
This is the main class that runs the entire game.
GameTest
This class that inherits Professor Duvall's DukeApplicationTest and implements each of our game's tests.
KeyHandler
This class initializes how the game responds to key input.
Laser
This class inherits the abstract Projectile class, implementing a basic projectile that does one damage.
Level
This is an abstract class that is used to create all types of levels used in this game.
Missile
This class inherits the abstract Projectile class, implementing a more powerful projectile that does two damage.
MissilePowerUp
This class inherits the abstract PowerUp class, implementing the ability for the spaceship to shoot missiles that do more damage.
MovingObject
This is an abstract class that is used for all moving objects on the screen, including the entities and projectiles.
PowerUp
This is an abstract class that is used for the BurstFire, Missile, and SpaceshipSpeed PowerUps.
Projectile
This is an abstract class used by its subclasses to create Projectiles that can collide with Entities in the game and do damage.
Spaceship
This class inherits the abstract entity class, which is used to create a spaceship object.
SpaceshipSpeedPowerUp
This class inherits the abstract PowerUp class, implementing the ability for the spaceship to move faster on key press.
StatusDisplay
This class is used to display all information and messages on the screen, including level information and menus.
